%N A394965 Decimal expansion of Pi^3/360.
%H A394965 H. F. Sandham, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1090/S0002-9939-1954-0062248-X">Some infinite series</a>, Proc. Amer. Math. Soc., Vol. 5 (1954), pp. 430-436.
%F A394965 Equals Sum_{k>=1} (-1)^(k+1)/(k^3*sinh(k*Pi)) (Sandham, 1954, p. 430, eq. 1.32). Note that equation 1.32 has an error: the powers 1^5, 2^5, 3^5, ... should be 1^3, 2^3, 3^3, ... .
